{
  "texts": [
    "These activation values can be interpreted as the significance of the region associated with a particular category within the input image.",
    "By weighting and summing the input feature mapping values of the last layer of the residual unit, the CAM can be obtained.",
    "In the calculation, it is assumed that f k (x, y) represents the activation of the spatial position coordinate point (x, y) in the last residual cell of channel k.",
    "With channel k, the result of the GAP that has been performed is denoted as F k, and F k is",
    "x,y f k (x, y)."
  ]
}